===Proper noun===
'''''Acer'''''

# A [[botanical name]] at the rank of genus. [[Circumscription]] of this genus ''Acer'' has been fairly stable over the past few decades - the [[maple]]s. Placement is either in [[family]] ''[[Aceraceae]]'' or family ''[[Sapindaceae]]''. 

